  // Main layout
  main
    .container
      // Section: Main info
      section.mt-5.wow.fadeIn
        // Grid row
        .row
          // Grid column
          .col-md-6.mb-4
            img.img-fluid.z-depth-1-half(src='https://mdbootstrap.com/img/Marketing/mdb-press-pack/mdb-main.jpg' alt)
          // Grid column
          // Grid column
          .col-md-6.mb-4
            //  Main heading 
            h3.h3.mb-3 Material Design for Bootstrap
            p
              | This template is created with Material Design for Bootstrap (

              strong MDB
              |  ) framework.
            p Read details below to learn more about MDB.
            //  Main heading 
            hr
            p
              strong 400+
              |  material UI elements,

              strong 600+
              |  material icons,

              strong 74
              |  CSS animations, SASS files, templates, tutorials and many more.

              strong Free for personal and commercial use.
            //  CTA 
            a.btn.btn-grey.btn-md(target='_blank' href='https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/jquery/getting-started/download/')
              | Download

              i.fas.fa-download.ml-1
            a.btn.btn-grey.btn-md(target='_blank' href='https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/jquery/components/')
              | Live demo

              i.far.fa-image.ml-1
          // Grid column
        // Grid row
      // Section: Main info
      hr.my-5
      // Section: Main features & Quick Start
      section
        h3.h3.text-center.mb-5 About MDB
        // Grid row
        .row.wow.fadeIn
          // Grid column
          .col-lg-6.col-md-12.px-4
            // First row
            .row
              .col-1.mr-3
                i.fas.fa-code.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h5.feature-title Bootstrap 4
                p.grey-text Thanks to MDB you can take advantage of all feature of newest Bootstrap 4.
            // /First row
            div(style='height:30px')
            // Second row
            .row
              .col-1.mr-3
                i.fas.fa-book.fa-2x.blue-text
              .col-10
                h5.feature-title Detailed documentation
                p.grey-text.
                  We give you detailed user-friendly documentation at your disposal. It will help you to implement your ideas easily.
                  
            // /Second row
            div(style='height:30px')
            // Third row
            .row
              .col-1.mr-3
                i.fas.fa-graduation-cap.fa-2x.cyan-text
              .col-10
                h5.feature-title Lots of tutorials
                p.grey-text We care about the development of our users. We have prepared numerous tutorials, which allow you to learn how to use MDB as well as other technologies.
            // /Third row
          // /Grid column
          // Grid column
          .col-lg-6.col-md-12
            p.h5.text-center.mb-4 Watch our "5 min Quick Start" tutorial
            .embed-responsive.embed-responsive-16by9
              iframe.embed-responsive-item(src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/cXTThxoywNQ' allowfullscreen)
          // /Grid column
        // /Grid row
      // Section: Main features & Quick Start
      hr.my-5
      // Section: Not enough
      section
        h2.my-5.h3.text-center Not enough?
        // First row
        .row.features-small.mb-5.mt-3.wow.fadeIn
          // First column
          .col-md-4
            // First row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title Free for personal and commercial use
                p.grey-text.
                  Our license is user-friendly. Feel free to use MDB for both private as well as commercial projects.
                  
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /First row
            // Second row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title 400+ UI elements
                p.grey-text.
                  An impressive collection of flexible components allows you to develop any project.
                  
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /Second row
            // Third row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title 600+ icons
                p.grey-text Hundreds of useful, scalable, vector icons at your disposal.
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /Third row
            // Fourth row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title Fully responsive
                p.grey-text It doesn't matter whether your project will be displayed on desktop, laptop, tablet or mobile phone. MDB looks great on each screen.
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /Fourth row
          // /First column
          // Second column
          .col-md-4.flex-center
            img.z-depth-0.img-fluid(src='https://mdbootstrap.com/img/Others/screens.png' alt='MDB Magazine Template displayed on iPhone')
          // /Second column
          // Third column
          .col-md-4.mt-2
            // First row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title 70+ CSS animations
                p.grey-text.
                  Neat and easy to use animations, which will increase the interactivity of your project and delight your visitors.
                  
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /First row
            // Second row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title Plenty of useful templates
                p.grey-text Need inspiration? Use one of our predefined templates for free.
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /Second row
            // Third row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title Easy installation
                p.grey-text.
                  5 minutes, a few clicks and... done. You will be surprised at how easy it is.
                  
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /Third row
            // Fourth row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.indigo-text
              .col-10
                h6.feature-title Easy to use and customize
                p.grey-text Using MDB is straightforward and pleasant. Components flexibility allows you deep customization. You will easily adjust each component to suit your needs.
                div(style='height:15px')
            // /Fourth row
          // /Third column
        // /First row
      // Section: Not enough
      hr.mb-5
      // Section: More
      section
        h2.my-5.h3.text-center ...and even more
        // First row
        .row.features-small.mt-5.wow.fadeIn
          // Grid column
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6
            // Grid row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fab.fa-firefox.fa-2x.mb-1.indigo-text(aria-hidden='true')
              .col-10.mb-2.pl-3
                h5.feature-title.font-bold.mb-1 Cross-browser compatibility
                p.grey-text.mt-2.
                  Chrome, Firefox, IE, Safari, Opera, Microsoft Edge - MDB loves all browsers; all browsers love MDB.
                  
            // /Grid row
          // /Grid column
          // Grid column
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6
            // Grid row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-level-up-alt.fa-2x.mb-1.indigo-text(aria-hidden='true')
              .col-10.mb-2
