            // /Grid row
          // /Grid column
          // Grid column
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6
            // Grid row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-code.fa-2x.mb-1.indigo-text(aria-hidden='true')
              .col-10.mb-2
                h5.feature-title.font-bold.mb-1 jQuery 3.x
                p.grey-text.mt-2.
                  MDB is integrated with newest jQuery. Therefore you can use all the latest features which come along with it.
                  
            // /Grid row
          // /Grid column
        // /First row
        // Second row
        .row.features-small.mt-4.wow.fadeIn
          // Grid column
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6
            // Grid row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-cubes.fa-2x.mb-1.indigo-text(aria-hidden='true')
              .col-10.mb-2
                h5.feature-title.font-bold.mb-1 Modularity
                p.grey-text.mt-2 Material Design for Bootstrap comes with both, compiled, ready to use libraries including all features as well as modules for CSS (SASS files) and JS.
            // /Grid row
          // /Grid column
          // Grid column
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6
            // Grid row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-question.fa-2x.mb-1.indigo-text(aria-hidden='true')
              .col-10.mb-2
                h5.feature-title.font-bold.mb-1 Technical support
                p.grey-text.mt-2.
                  We care about reliability. If you have any questions - do not hesitate to contact us.
                  
            // /Grid row
          // /Grid column
          // Grid column
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6
            // Grid row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.fas.fa-th.fa-2x.mb-1.indigo-text(aria-hidden='true')
              .col-10.mb-2
                h5.feature-title.font-bold.mb-1 Flexbox
                p.grey-text.mt-2 MDB fully supports Flex Box. You can forget about alignment issues.
            // /Grid row
          // /Grid column
          // Grid column
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6
            // Grid row
            .row
              .col-2
                i.far.fa-file-code.fa-2x.mb-1.indigo-text(aria-hidden='true')
              .col-10.mb-2
                h5.feature-title.font-bold.mb-1 SASS files
                p.grey-text.mt-2.
                  Arranged and well documented .scss files can't wait until you compile them.
                  
            // /Grid row
          // /Grid column
        // /Second row
